quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  98,1,lm yakun aladhin kafaruu min alyhwd walnsara walmushrikin tarkyn kufruhum hataa tatiahum aleallamat alty wueidu biha fi alkutub alsabqt
  98,2,"why rasul allah muhamad salaa allah ealayh wslm, yatlu qranana fi suhuf mthrt"
  98,3,"fy tilk alsuhuf 'akhbar sadqt wa'awamir eadlt, tahdi 'iilaa alhaqi wa'iilaa sirat mstqym"
  98,4,"wma akhtalaf aladhin 'uwtuu alkitab min alyhwd walnsara fi kawn muhamad salaa allah ealayh wasalam rasulana hqana; lamaa yajidunah min neth fi ktabhm, 'iilaa min baed ma tbynu 'anah alnabii aldhy wueidu bih fi altawrat wal'injyl, fakanuu mjtmeyn ealaa sihat nbwth, falamaa bueith jhdwha wtfrraqu"
  98,5,"wama 'umiruu fi sayr alshraye 'iilaa liaebuduu allah wahdah qasdyn bieibadatihim wjhh, maylyn ean alshirk 'iilaa al'iyman, wayuqimuu alslat, wyuaddu alzkat, wdhlk hu din alastqamt, wahu al'islam"
  98,6,"'in aladhin kafaruu min alyhwd walnsara walmushrikin eqabhm nar jahanam khalidin fyha, 'uwlayik hum 'ashadu alkhlyqt shra"
  98,7,"'in aladhin saddaqu allah watabaeuu rasulih waeamiluu alsalhat, 'uwlayik hum khayr alkhlq"
  98,8,"jzawhm eind rabihim yawm alqiamat janaat 'iiqamat waistiqrar fi mntha alhsn, tajri min taht qswrha alanhar, khalidin fiha abdana, radi allah eanhum fqbl 'aemalahum alsalht, waraduu eanh bima aedd lahum min 'anwae alkramat, dhlk aljaza' alhasan liman khaf allah wajtnb measyh"